  id: 39
  title: "Ghi ch\xE9p thu\u1ED1c gi\u1EA3i #4 \u2014 Ca nhi\u1EC5m \u0111\u1EA7u
    ti\xEAn"
  category: 6
  content: "H\u1ED3 s\u01A1 y t\u1EBF \u2014 Khu quarantine qu\xE2n \u0111\u1ED9i.
    B\u1EC7nh nh\xE2n #001 (gi\u1EA5u t\xEAn): nam, 28 tu\u1ED5i, nh\u1EADp khu c\xE1ch
    ly sau ti\u1EBFp x\xFAc v\u1EDBi b\u1EC7nh nh\xE2n zero t\u1EA1i b\u1EC7nh vi\u1EC7n.
    Tri\u1EC7u ch\u1EE9ng: s\u1ED1t cao 39\xB0C, ho khan, sau 6 gi\u1EDD b\u1EAFt
    \u0111\u1EA7u co gi\u1EADt, sau 12 gi\u1EDD m\u1EA5t nh\u1EADn th\u1EE9c, sau
    18 gi\u1EDD bi\u1EBFn \u0111\u1ED5i ho\xE0n to\xE0n. Th\u1EDDi gian \u1EE7 b\u1EC7nh
    \u01B0\u1EDBc t\xEDnh 2-4 gi\u1EDD t\u1EEB l\xFAc ti\u1EBFp x\xFAc. KH\xD4NG
    c\xF3 thu\u1ED1c. Khuy\u1EBFn ngh\u1ECB: c\xE1ch ly tuy\u1EC7t \u0111\u1ED1i
    24 gi\u1EDD, n\u1EBFu sau 24 gi\u1EDD kh\xF4ng c\xF3 tri\u1EC7u ch\u1EE9ng th\xEC
    an to\xE0n."
  image: {fileID: 0}
  voiceLog: {fileID: 0}
